{"tid":261512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[真人真事]點解而加香港人咁撚冷血？","createTime":"2017-05-28T13:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T03:47:24.000Z","uid":97606,"like":12,"dislike":124,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ffa97518af340a1b039b15c051208010cd23312","tid":261512,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:50:53.000Z","msg":"琴日搞project搞到今朝6點先訓，結果下晝4點先起身，<br />\n琴晚放左學補習補得夜又無食過dinner，姐係差唔多有24粒鐘無食過野，<br />\n起左身落街諗住買野食，老豆老母唔係屋企，<br />\n結果血糖低行左無耐就暈左，去到8點幾先醒翻，<br />\n屌你老味我起身果下好似如夢初醒咁唔知發生咩事，原來我仲訓緊係條街到，天都黑鳩晒，<br />\n我個頭仲撞到地下腫左一噠添，<br />\n我暈果到唔算偏僻，點解大街大巷見到有人暈左都可以唔理？訓左係到3個幾鐘都無人理？<br />\n翻到去仲要俾老豆老母屌我出街玩唔留字條，真係頂你個肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab55c49c068d4361c14276eeaa304f8f590f12e","tid":261512,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:53:52.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"40dd44896d199865b8299562c8ebf8d882826a03","tid":261512,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:54:03.000Z","msg":"唔係咁誇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c9cb0339e534940f8ab3de9c8cf13e6e01a5cb","tid":261512,"uid":53798,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:54:24.000Z","msg":"首先你自己都有錯, 咁虛弱都唔搵屋企人<br />\n<br />\n另外如果你成個毒友, 酒鬼既話, 的確會無人理<br />\n<br />\n而家香港仲邊有香港人"},{"pid":"48b52f53632e93be8411e1e23bc87911cd6d90be","tid":261512,"uid":51200,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:54:43.000Z","msg":"時事台？<br />\n叫春就死去感情台啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe095ecb5cc7606e7308d1ea7e66601b35715b02","tid":261512,"uid":29549,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:55:03.000Z","msg":"24小時冇食過野自己唔識買野食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgm